Output terminal.gif
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Width 700
Set Height 380
Set FontSize 14
Set Padding 10
Set Framerate 30
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.2

Type "docker compose up -d"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "  agentic-rag ............ running"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Type "  ollama ................. running"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Type "  langfuse ............... running"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Type "  postgresql ............. running"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Type "  redis .................. running"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Sleep 800ms
Type "python -m agentic_rag"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "  RAG pipeline ............ [READY]"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Type "  LangGraph ............... [READY]"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Type "  Qdrant .................. [LIVE]"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Type "  Langfuse traces ......... [READY]"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Sleep 800ms
Type 'echo "All systems nominal."'
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "All systems nominal."
Sleep 500ms
Enter
